title: Earth Food Store Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Salad bar, Juice bar, Take-out
description: Vegetarian cafe serves organic salads, soups, frittata, tarts and a hot dish which changes with seasonal produce. Has vegan options. Also serves juices, coffee, muffins and buffins (gluten free, egg, dairy and sugar free muffins). Carries organic fruit, vegetables and grocery items for sale.
